git clone --bare https://github.com/kaykhan/.dotfiles.git $HOME/.dotfiles
alias dotfiles='/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/.dotfiles/ --work-tree=$HOME'


1. Workspace shortcuts

Settings -> Keyboard -> View/Customise Shortcuts -> Navigation -> Move to workspace on left/right

2. Unite Shell gnome extention (hide top bar)

https://github.com/hardpixel/unite-shell

3. gnome-tweaks

keyboard & mouse -> Accleeration Profile -> Flat 

Theme

sudo apt install polybar

install hide top bar > intelli hide toggle on both

